    "If the confidence value is high, then the reliability of the rule is high.",
    "There is a higher likelihood of Wj occurring when Wi is present.",
    "The process involving the ARM consists of two steps.",
    "The first step is to find frequent itemsets where the support value of all the itemsets is above the minimum support value.",
    "The second step is to generate the association rules using the output of step 1 while discarding the rules below the minimum confidence value."
